DNS
Domain Name System
system store info's about domains in DB in place uncenter on internet
1- ( Your PC ) : Where is www.example.com ? -> to ISP DNS Server
2- ( ISP DNS Server ) : it is 66.115.210.3! -> to Your PC
3 - ( Your PC ) : i will go to 66.115.210.3! -> to Webserver at 66.115.210.3
4 - (Webserver at 66...) : Here is your web content! (show webpage in your browser)
Ping
To Know if device wake up or not
By your pc send request to server, if server reply it's wake up